Women's Fitness - August 2014  UK

124 Pages | True PDF | English | 31 MB 


Women's Fitness magazine is the ultimate fitness title for the modern, busy woman who wants to look and feel her best without spending hours in the gym. Ideal for all ages and fitness levels, it features workouts, training tips, celebrity fitness secrets and nutrition advice for women who want to make the most of their limited time for exercise.
